title: ask for a critique to a plan
pid: 38797ab6-c924-4d5e-ba4d-e80a28420f4e
body: |2-
  Can you find beef with [[PLAN]]?
  Beefs of interest include:

  - incorrect things
  - awkward or inelegant things
  - dangerous things
  - missing concepts or abstractions 9esp. types)
    if they would make things safer or clearer

  Please put what beef you find in a sibling document, 4_critique.org.
